text: "Jailhouse Rock" is a 1957 song by Elvis Presley. It was taken from the 1957 movie soundtrack Jailhouse Rock. It went to number 1 in the United Kingdom, the United States, Scotland and South Africa, number 3 in Australia, number 7 in Finland and number 19 in the Netherlands.
